{"tid":1279740,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係街望到個靚女 忍唔住係咁望佢","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:43:07.000Z","uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ca90408bc798bfe0b304ff0b0f0691c4697c24","tid":1279740,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"個女仔又唔係靚到沊一聲個隻靚，而係個樣好順眼，好吸引你一直望落去果隻樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁嗰時係地鐵佢企我對面，雙方互望咗一眼，我即刻怕醜到耷返頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後襯佢玩緊電話嘅時候偷望多佢幾眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我估佢應該二十尾，傳統OL look，真係好正，如果佢可以做我老婆就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我淨係見到佢中指有戴戒指，姐係未結婚！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然大我幾年我都ok！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後隔一個站就有個毒撚上咗車，條友係四眼矇豬眼嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難聽啲講係連望都會覺得心情差咗嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁佢一上車就即刻係度睄我老婆，嗰時我即刻望到我老婆斜視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇唔起嗰種樣，我就一路忍笑，一路偷偷地望我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至少我老婆冇斜視我，淨係啤住個毒撚，我係咪都唔算好毒咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105074b90f2f00e5a31327d15c5762fb18f6b2ee","tid":1279740,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"真係好吸引人望呀老婆bb 可惜我已經唔係個記得佢個樣，淨係覺得佢個樣好順眼，又純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb73c56eb2fa2b5d280e0c81a968c7fe6259ffab","tid":1279740,"uid":249088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f62cd6394dacf81ccd5be2bf9eab7842464afea","tid":1279740,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105074b90f2f00e5a31327d15c5762fb18f6b2ee","tid":1279740,"uid":20574